---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import kaiMcKimImage from '../assets/kaimckim.png';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Kai McKim - Tutor at New Leaf Academy" description="Meet Kai McKim, a specialist English tutor at New Leaf Academy." />
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<div class="bio-container">
				<div class="bio-header">
					<Image
						src={kaiMcKimImage}
						alt="Kai McKim, Tutor at New Leaf Academy"
						class="bio-headshot"
						width={200}
						height={200}
					/>
					<div class="header-text">
						<h1>Kai McKim</h1>
						<p class="role">Specialist English Tutor</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="bio-content">
					<h2>About Kai</h2>
					<p>
						Having received top grades in my GCSEs and A-Levels, including A*s in English Literature and Language, I went on to study architecture at The Bartlett at UCL.					
					</p>
					<p>
						Towards the end of my degree, I was asked to give lectures to first-year students. It was then that I discovered how much I enjoyed teaching and passing on knowledge. Since starting to tutor online in 2024, my love of English has only deepened. With a passion for the subject that keeps me constantly reading and writing, I find it easy to share my enthusiasm with my students.					
					</p>
					<p>
						I am proud that my students have often achieved results better than anyone expected. It’s incredibly rewarding to help them realise their potential. I believe every student has the ability to succeed in English, and I am committed to helping them do just that.					
					</p>
					<p>
						When I’m not tutoring, I enjoy putting my architectural skills to practical use. I recently completed a project building a studio in my garden from scratch, which was an amazing test of patience, hard work, and creative design.					
					</p>
				</div>
                <div class="cta-section">
                    <h2>Ready to Start Your Journey?</h2>
                    <p>Dan is ready to help you or your child achieve academic success. Book a friendly, no-obligation chat today.</p>
                    <a href="/consultations" class="cta-button">
                        Book Your Free Consultation and Taster Session
                    </a>
                </div>
			</div>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	:root {
		--card-bg-color: #f9f9f9;
        --box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
	}

	main {
		max-width: 900px;
		margin: 2em auto;
		padding: 0 1em;
		box-sizing: border-box;
		color: var(--accent);
	}

	.bio-container {
		background-color: var(--card-bg-color);
		padding: 2em;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
	}

	.bio-header {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		align-items: center;
		text-align: center;
		margin-bottom: 2em;
		gap: 1em;
	}

	.bio-headshot {
		width: clamp(150px, 30vw, 200px);
		height: clamp(150px, 30vw, 200px);
		object-fit: cover;
		border-radius: 50%;
		border: 5px solid var(--accent);
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
	}

	.header-text h1 {
		font-size: clamp(2em, 6vw, 2.8em);
		margin: 0;
		color: var(--accent);
	}

	.header-text .role {
		font-size: clamp(1.1em, 3vw, 1.3em);
		font-weight: bold;
		color: var(--accent-pop);
		margin-top: 0.25em;
	}

	.bio-content h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.5em, 5vw, 2em);
		color: var(--accent);
		border-bottom: 2px solid #e9eafc;
		padding-bottom: 0.5em;
		margin-bottom: 1em;
	}

	.bio-content p {
		font-size: clamp(1em, 2vw, 1.1em);
		line-height: 1.8;
		margin-bottom: 1.5em;
	}

        .cta-section {
		text-align: center;
		margin-top: 2em;
		padding: 2em;
		background-color: white;
		border-radius: 12px;
		box-shadow: var(--box-shadow);
		color: var(--accent);
	}
	
	.cta-section h2 {
		font-size: clamp(1.5em, 4vw, 1.8em);
		margin-top: 0;
		color: var(--accent);
	}

    .cta-section p {
        margin-bottom: 1.5em;
    }

	.cta-button {
		display: inline-block;
		padding: 1em 2em;
		background-color: var(--accent-pop);
		color: white;
		font-weight: bold;
		text-decoration: none;
		border-radius: 8px;
		box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
		transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
	}

	.cta-button:hover {
		transform: translateY(-5px);
		box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
	}

	@media (min-width: 768px) {
		.bio-header {
			flex-direction: row;
			text-align: left;
			gap: 2em;
		}
	}
</style>
